; Regression test for issue #844: Cleared records don't get checked when using --strict or --pedantic (BZ#844)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/844
;
; --strict and --pedantic should check ALL transactions including cleared ones.
; Previously, cleared transactions (marked with *) were skipped during account validation.

account Assets:Cash
account Expenses:Food

2024/01/01 * Cleared payee
    Expenses:Unknown    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal --pedantic -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 11:
While parsing posting:
  Expenses:Unknown    $10.00

Error: Unknown account 'Expenses:Unknown'
end test

test bal --strict
             $-10.00  Assets:Cash
              $10.00  Expenses:Unknown
--------------------
                   0
__ERROR__
Warning: "$FILE", line 11: Unknown account 'Expenses:Unknown'
Warning: "$FILE", line 11: Unknown commodity '$'
end test
